data.description: Open House Feb.4th 2.00-4.00pm.Quality Built by Powell Custom Homes.Beautiful Two Story home with 4/5 bedrooms,2+ bathrooms  located in Mattawan,s Woodfield Subdivision.Situated on a 1 acre lot. Home sits at the end of a Cul de sac .Features include 3 car garage with deep 3rd stall and workshop behind 2 car,Inground pool,New roof,New carpet,main floor laundry.Nice open kitchen with appliances included. Gas Log Fireplace.Wired for surround sound in living room.Huge Bonus room 20 x 22 could be 5th bedroom.Wired for generator.Underground sprinkling.Outdoor speakers for pool area.Whole house  home warranty incl.well and pool pump valid till 11/13/2025.Large side yard outside the fenced in yard with a bonfire pit.Septic system replaced 2016.Natural gas grill hookupsHigh Speed Internet.
